  <notes>
    The Dataverse `data=` convention typically wraps an opaque string the custom page interprets. Treat it as JSON first; if `JSON.parse` throws, fall back to URL-decoded direct params. Document this dual path in the hook's JSDoc so future maintainers understand.

    The `associatedTo` shape is `{entity, id}` per FR-19 Surface 1 (ribbon launches from a related-record subgrid carry the parent record's entity + id). The Wave 1 `<SendEmailPage />` wrapper accepts an `associations` prop that this parser maps into.

    UQ from spec (none directly addressed here; FR-18 is well-specified).
  </notes>

